# Supermatter Engine

Supermatter is an extremely dangerous crystal-based power source.

## What It Does
- Generates large amounts of power when properly managed.
- Interacts strongly with surrounding gases and heat.

## Core Requirements
- Reliable atmospheric setup and gas handling.
- Stable cooling strategy.
- Continuous monitoring and emergency response plans.

## Safety Priorities
- Keep unauthorized personnel away from the crystal chamber.
- Monitor delamination warning signs continuously.
- Prepare containment and evacuation contingencies in advance.

Supermatter operation should only be attempted by trained engineers with station-level coordination.
